
# Function


## ```js tmpDir ```


Return the os temp directory path



## Example (js)

```js
const tmpDir = require('@coffeekraken/node/fs/tmpDir');
tmpDir(); // => '/private/var/folders/3x/jf5977fn79jbglr7rk0tq4d00000gn/T'
```
